### Obtener eventos activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/eventos/activos
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener eventos por ciudad
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/eventos/ciudad/bogota
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener eventos por equipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/eventos/equipo/eq-001
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Marcar evento como inactivo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/eventos/ev-001/inactivar
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json 